![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/23d15765-4e59-4048-8fb3-221d1c9f50f3/15340.jpg)

Absolutely CHAOTIC start to AEW Dynamite that saw multiple storylines weaved in, Paul Heyman style.

Gabe Kidd starts the show by calling out Darby Allin, who attacks immediately.

Coffin Drop to the outside. Darby pulls out a THUMBTACK SKATEBOARD, Wheeler Yuta tries to get involved but he takes the brunt of the skateboard attack.

The Death Riders make their way out, with Moxley look disappointed in Wheeler Yuta. Before they can attack, the lights go out and HOOK arrives.

But Hook isn't able to help because the Opps run out past him to brawl with the Death Riders. Willow Nightengale runs out to take down Marina Shafir.

Darby and Gabe Kidd brawl to the back of the ECW Arena where Darby puts Gabe in a body bag and ties him to a truck. Then drives off with Gabe Kidd still attached

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1f3f3917-5c4b-42fd-b591-339ad39c18b8/15346.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/02d0b32b-4dd4-4ab6-a76a-47df39710ddf/15348.jpg)

## **_RIHO IS BACK!!!!!!_**

*   ## **_TBS CHAMPIONSHIP: Mercedes Moné def. Alex Windsor_**
    

Post match Mercedes Moné refuses to give Alex Windsor a handshake, Alex attacks but Mercedes cracks her with the belt and puts her in the Bank Statement

AND THEN RIHO RETURNS!!! RIHO takes out Mercedes Moné and poses with the TNT Championship

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0064418b-cb85-433e-8cd3-7e8f9fc62dfd/processed_15354.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9954d9e9-65a2-4b93-b35d-966dc5803e88/15359.jpg)

Hook is furious with the Opps. They replaced him before his body was even cold. Hobbs is about to fight when Joe asks him to wait

Joe knows Hook is mad. They did replace him. Joe made the call because the opportunity was calling and Hook wasn't ready. But Hobbs was.

Joe tells Hook that he understands how he feels. But if Hook ever needs help, he won't have to call the Opps. Because they will always have his back whether he wants it or not.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a75b6ea0-d606-47c5-a84c-2f3fe63b7ed3/15358.jpg)

Ricochet says if anybody has been paying attention, his issue with the Hurt Syndicate started long ago. Ricochet tried to join the group, they called him a kiss ass and threatened him. The Syndicate is washed. All they are is legacy. Ricochet wants to take their legacy from them.

He's done with the games and he wants a Trios match with the HS at All Out. This is not a request. It's a demand

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/db53dd2c-967b-4d51-ae4d-ee6b72fe0995/15362.jpg)

Mark Briscoe vs Konosuke Takeshita is set for Collision this Saturday.

Mark Briscoe called out Don Callis for a shot at Kyle Fletcher's TNT Championship but Callis says he needs to beat a member of the family first. Mark says send whoever

Callis has chosen Konosuke Takeshita. But Mark wants to fight NOW. So Callis gives him Lance Archer.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d9e59e93-02ee-436b-868c-60df5be0b18d/15363.jpg)

*   ## **_MARK BRISCOE DEF. LANCE ARCHER_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/17fbcb7b-ece4-40c0-97f1-cda6033b798e/15364.jpg)

## "**_GOD DOESN'T JUDGE... THAT'S MY JOB_**."

Toni Storm has defeated belt collectors and forever champions. This championship is here golden cross to bare. She is begging any woman with a pulse to step up and take this championship from her.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8eb9828b-1b4b-4be5-a669-35caa864f987/15373.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW Tag Team Championships: Brodido def. Death Riders_**
    

Great match that sees Jon Moxley and Marina Shafir almost cost Brodido the titles before Darby Allin runs out to take down Moxley and even the odds.

Bandido hits a 21-plex on Yuta for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ebe04803-4d86-47da-96d3-abb72e055861/15375.jpg)

Renee Paquette asks Okada what was up between him and Takeshita last week.

Okada says everyone knows he's the Rainmaker and what he's about. Kazuchika Okada is the top dog in the Don Callis Family.... bitch.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7ca9197a-b7b6-4440-a6d6-ef810ba35a80/15377.jpg)

MVP can't wait to step back in the ring alongside his brothers. The Hurt Syndicate accepts Ricochet's challenge.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1adbce8e-5c83-487b-aad3-79bd4d48a601/15381.jpg)

Adam Copeland was out for a second but FTR jumped him and Christian came out almost immediately. A big pull apart brawl occurs.

But an interesting moment happens where Dax Harwood mistakes independent wrestling standout Adam Priest for a regular jobber who's trying to break up the fight.

Dax shoves Priest by the faces and now PRIEST AND DAX are brawling.

The fight is broken up to end the segment

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3d9070e9-8960-4127-90d4-4719518985e6/15384.jpg)

Stokley and FTR are trying to cut a promo on Cope and Christian when Adam Priest walks up.

Cash tells Adam he has had a SINGLE match on AEW TV, where does he get off?

Priest needs to find himself a tag team partner for this Saturday, FTR will make him famous.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8348b36b-80b5-4acb-9fc1-970d649f095a/processed_15397.jpg)

*   ## **_ALL STAR 8 MAN TAG: Don Callis Family and Young Bucks def. Kenny Omega, Hangman Adam Page and JETSPEED_**
    

High octane. High impact match that saw everything you'd expect plus a call back to the legendary Revolution 2020 Hangman and Kenny vs Young Bucks match.

Post match, brutal beatdown as the DCF takes out Kenny Omega with a Brainbuster through a table on the outside.